Ques 1: OTT Subscription Management System

Project Overview
----------------
Develop a Spring Core application to manage OTT subscriptions where users can activate plans from different streaming platforms.

Requirements
The application should support multiple OTT providers such as Netflix, Amazon Prime, and Hotstar for subscription activation. 
Use @Qualifier to inject the selected OTT provider and process the subscription request.

Flow
User chooses an OTT platform
System selects the corresponding subscription provider
Selected subscription plan gets activated